<h2>Treatment for ptosis</h2><p>Your child will need <a href="/healthaz/ophthalmology/ptosis-surgery/">surgery</a> if the ptosis affects their vision. Different types of surgeries can correct ptosis. Your eye doctor will discuss with you which surgery is best for your child and the risks involved with any surgery.</p> </div>
</div>
